sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import {Link} from "react-router-dom"; const CourseRow = ( { deleteCourse, course, lastModified="1/1/2021", title="CS1111", owner="Alex" }) => { return ( {course.title} {course.owner} {course.lastModified} deleteCourse(course)} className="fas fa-trash"> ) } export default CourseRow
